OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779274977
OL,3,CDog rescued by RNLI after falling onto
OL,4,Crocks from coastal path
OL,6,FIlfracombe's lifeboat crew came to the
OL,7,Frescue of a dog after it became
OL,8,Fstranded on rocks.
OL,10,FThe pet had fallen from the coastal
OL,11,Fpath after becoming scared by another
OL,12,Fdog and slipping from her collar near
OL,13,FCapstone Hill, Ilfracombe, on Friday
OL,14,Fafternoon (15 May).
OL,16,FShe was surrounded by rough water and
OL,17,FRNLI crews got as close as they could
OL,18,Fby boat before one of the team swam
OL,19,Fthe rest of the way.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
